      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772381476426,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Flow of Content ->\n    First Devops, How we will deploy our APP(Linux, Networking, AWS) + HLD -> \n    ML + ML-OPs + LLM + LLM-OPs\n    Containerisation(Kubernetis) + Automation\n    DSA + LLD -> till here 7 months\n    Frontend -> 45 days\n    \n    \n\nRecordings -> Go to Google Calender\n\nHelp -> Youtube\n        Google, GPT\n        Group\n        Direct Call\n\nWebsite -> use website only for DSA and complete all those questions, all are company asked \n            questions",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Flow of Content ->\n    First Devops, How we will deploy our APP(Linux, Networking, AWS) + HLD -> \n    ML + ML-OPs + LLM + LLM-OPs\n    Containerisation(Kubernetis) + Automation\n    DSA + LLD -> till here 7 months\n    Frontend -> 45 days\n    \n    \n\nRecordings -> Go to Google Calender\n\nHelp -> Youtube\n        Google, GPT\n        Group\n        Direct Call\n\nWebsite -> use website only for DSA and complete all those questions, all are company asked \n            questions",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
