      "updated": 1772386007659,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Since google.com is not have only one IP, it has n number of IP, what google will do, google\nwill club all their IPs and put a different location named as ANS (Authorative Name Server)\nand that IP we will get by our TLD server. Like wise other companies have also their own\nANS",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Since google.com is not have only one IP, it has n number of IP, what google will do, google\nwill club all their IPs and put a different location named as ANS (Authorative Name Server)\nand that IP we will get by our TLD server. Like wise other companies have also their own\nANS",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
