      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Tech, Tech + I -> write class content with image -> NO AI -> Media should be attached like video, pdf, pages\nMonday -> Tech\nTuesday. -> DSA + 1 post\nWednesday -> Tech\nThursday -> Twit\nFriday ->. DSA or Job Openings or Interview Experience, Anything Technical like top 10 Github, top 10 system design interview question like that\nSaturday -> Tech\nSunday -> Post 1 picture\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
