      "updated": 1772801773153,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Hook Line ->  this interview question make me selected, this interview question\n        not make me selected, I came across this question and I never expected\nthat this will be asked in interview., I learn these topics and it completely and\nit changed for me what backend engineering is, something like this, something which\ngenerated curiosity, One or two lines that generates curiosity, so that everyone can\nclick read more and start reading.\n\n2. 2 or 3 paragraph, not more that 2 or 3 lines more for each\n\n3. In these small paragraphs what we can write? -> we can write about, whatever the\n    post topic is just write about that.\n\n4 How to add hashtags/ Where to add Hashtags ->  somewhere in between paragraph put\n        1 or 2 hashtags so that our content can look more interesting. Not more hashtags\nin every or alternate para 1 hashtag. Write para in general term not in fancy or AI \ngenerated. We can be as Normal as we can like sometime Happy, sometime sad like that.\n\n5 At last we can give CTA(Call to Action) -> Here we can tell if you want to follow up\n    my technical journey and learn from this, you can follow me or comment this this this\n    OR write a post so that someone comment on own.\n\n6 For sprigboot learn from 10 to 12 hour video see fully and thats it.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Hook Line ->  this interview question make me selected, this interview question\n        not make me selected, I came across this question and I never expected\nthat this will be asked in interview., I learn these topics and it completely and\nit changed for me what backend engineering is, something like this, something which\ngenerated curiosity, One or two lines that generates curiosity, so that everyone can\nclick read more and start reading.\n\n2. 2 or 3 paragraph, not more that 2 or 3 lines more for each\n\n3. In these small paragraphs what we can write? -> we can write about, whatever the\n    post topic is just write about that.\n\n4 How to add hashtags/ Where to add Hashtags ->  somewhere in between paragraph put\n        1 or 2 hashtags so that our content can look more interesting. Not more hashtags\nin every or alternate para 1 hashtag. Write para in general term not in fancy or AI \ngenerated. We can be as Normal as we can like sometime Happy, sometime sad like that.\n\n5 At last we can give CTA(Call to Action) -> Here we can tell if you want to follow up\n    my technical journey and learn from this, you can follow me or comment this this this\n    OR write a post so that someone comment on own.\n\n6 For sprigboot learn from 10 to 12 hour video see fully and thats it.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
